**HTML Form**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Simple HTML Form</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Simple HTML Form</h1>
  <form action="submit.php" method="post">
    <label for="name">Name:</label>
